      "span_text": "Extensive phylogenetic analysis based on full HA gene (1701 nt) and complete genome (13158nt: concatenated eight segments) were carried out by including 45 and 65 globally diverse H1N1pdm sequences (Table  S1 ) respectively using MrBayes version 3.1.2 [CITATION_2] ."
